Join the Club
We want you to experience all that our clubs have to offer. We would love to provide you with a personalized tour and can arrange a time for you to enjoy our various amenities. All Memberships include primary, spouse, and dependent children 26 and younger.
Please complete the inquiry form and we'll be in touch soon!
CLICK HERE FOR LIFESTYLE BROCHURE FOR INDIAN SPRING COUNTRY CLUB
CLICK HERE FOR LIFESTYLE BROCHURE FOR FOUNTAINS COUNTRY CLUB
DUAL ALL-INCLUSIVE GOLF MEMBERSHIP
Enjoy full access to our 3 18-hole golf courses including greens fees and practice facilities for everyone listed on the membership. Full access to the pool, fitness center, tennis courts, and social/dining events is also included. You may invite a guest to play if the guest has not played more than 6 times during the year, with current guest fees. This category also includes ancillary fees such as bag storage, locker fees, cart fees, admin fee, and amenity fees.
DUAL FULL GOLF MEMBERSHIP
Enjoy full access to our 3 18-hole golf courses including greens fees and practice facilities for everyone listed on the membership. Full access to the pool, fitness center, tennis courts, and social/dining events is also included. You may invite a guest to play if the guest has not played more than 6 times during the year, with current guest fees.
DUAL AFTERNOON MEMBERSHIP (tee times after 11AM)
Enjoy full access after 11am to our 3 18-hole golf courses including greens fees and practice facilities for everyone listed on the membership. Full access to the pool, fitness center, tennis courts, and social/dining events is also included. You may invite a guest to play if the guest has not played more than 6 times during the year, with current guest fees.
DUAL EXECUTIVE GOLF MEMBERSHIP (AGES 46-55)
Enjoy full access to our 3 18-hole golf courses and practice facilities for everyone listed on the membership. Full access to the pool, fitness center, tennis courts, and social/dining events along with indoor and outdoor dining is also included.
DUAL JUNIOR EXECUTIVE GOLF MEMBERSHIP (AGES 45 & UNDER)
Enjoy full access to our 3 18-hole golf courses and practice facilities for everyone listed on the membership. Full access to the pool, fitness center, tennis courts, and social/dining events along with indoor and outdoor dining is also included.
DUAL SOCIAL MEMBERSHIP
Enjoy full access to the fitness center, tennis courts, pool, and social/dining events along with indoor and outdoor dining for everyone listed on the membership.

Discover a Resort Lifestyle Second to None at Two Premier Clubs
Discover a Resort Lifestyle Second to None at Two Premier Clubs
Indian Spring Country Club and Fountains Country Club offer something for everyone — from 18-hole golf courses designed to thrill avid golfers to year-round social events perfect for families with busy schedules, and even mouth-watering cuisine that will satisfy any foodie!
Indian Spring is a gated, meticulously landscaped, private membership country club community, where you can live the life you’ve always dreamed about, surrounded by friends who make you feel right at home. Located in the relaxed seaside town of Boynton Beach, this lush, 800-acre community showcases unrivaled recreational and social venues.
With two championship golf courses with rolling fairways and brush-cut greens, a state-of-the-art fitness facility, and casual and elegant dining establishments to satisfy every taste.
Fountains Country Club is a private country club established in 1972 in Palm Beach County, Florida. The Club is located on 865 beautifully landscaped acres within a prestigious and superbly maintained gated golf community in Lake Worth. The Sports Complex offers 12 Har-Tru surfaced courts, pickleball, bocce ball, 8,000 square foot state-of-the-art fitness center, and more for our Members to stay active. Lounge at our resort-style pool and enjoy lunch or happy hour at the Aqua Pool Bar & Grill.
Click here to inquire about membership today.
